      <h2 id="happy-thanksgiving-message-to-patients-expressions-of-gratitude">Happy Thanksgiving Message to Patients: Expressions of Gratitude</h2>
      <p></p>

<p>
  Looking for more Thanksgiving message ideas? Check out our guides for 
  <a href="/question/thanksgiving-quotes-and-message">Sharing Thanksgiving Quotes and Messages of Deepest Gratitude</a>, <a href="/question/happy-thanksgiving-message-to-staff">Celebrating a Happy Thanksgiving Message to Staff: Warmest Gratitude</a>, and <a href="/question/happy-thanksgiving-message-for-clients">Sharing Happy Thanksgiving Messages: Warmth & Gratitude</a> 
